erencedFiles` |\n| task dependency collapse from unit-level edges | `TestFromWaveplanTask_TaskDependsOnCollapsesFromUnitEdges`, `TestFromWaveplanTask_NoExternalDeps_EmptyDependsOn` |\n| unit depends_on passthrough | `TestFromWaveplanUnit_DependsOnFromUnit` |\n| empty plan path rejection | `TestFromWaveplanTask_EmptyPlanPath_ReturnsError`, `TestFromWaveplanUnit_EmptyPlanPath_ReturnsError` |\n| missing doc_ref rejection | `TestFromWaveplanTask_MissingDocRef_ReturnsError` |\n| source = \"waveplan\" | `TestCandidate_SourceIsWaveplan` |\n| structurally valid for estimator | `TestCandidate_StructurallyValidForEstimator` |\n\n**Verification:**\n```\ngo test ./internal/contextsize/adapter -v   → 13 PASS, 0 FAIL\ngo test ./internal/contextsize/... -v       → 28 PASS, 0 FAIL\ngo build ./internal/contextsize/...         → clean\n```\n\n","time":{"start":1778783301143,"end":1778783312126}}}
